(\code{\link[=mape_svr]{mape_svr()}}, \code{\link[=mape_sym_svr]{mape_sym_svr()}}, \code{\link[=rmspe_lssvr]{rmspe_lssvr()}}, \code{\link[=rmspe_sym_lssvr]{rmspe_sym_lssvr()}})
remain available but are slated for deprecation.
